what this is.

20:46.549 --> 20:49.204
And so they actually
found a woman,

20:49.248 --> 20:51.511
who was now a sex therapist,

20:53.295 --> 20:55.950
and we sat and
talked one morning,

20:55.993 --> 20:58.909
and the first question
