wanted, that you needed?"

21:03.610 --> 21:05.655
Because I knew by that time

21:05.699 --> 21:09.355
how incredibly difficult
the operations were

21:09.398 --> 21:14.098
and all of this psychological
journey that had to be taken.

21:14.142 --> 21:18.059
And I said what was it
that you needed so much?

21:19.452 --> 21:21.105
And she said,

21:21.149 --> 21:25.893
